<item>
            <title>[COMPRESS-507] Commons Compress cannot be built with JDK14 due to Pack200 removal</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/COMPRESS-507</link>
                <project id="12310904" key="COMPRESS">Commons Compress</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Oracle dropped Pack200 in JDK14 as per&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8232022&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8232022&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Someone expressed his will to maintain Pack200 here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mail.openjdk.java.net/pipermail/jdk-dev/2020-March/003979.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://mail.openjdk.java.net/pipermail/jdk-dev/2020-March/003979.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pfirmstone/Pack200-ex-openjdk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/pfirmstone/Pack200-ex-openjdk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13288591">COMPRESS-507</key>
            <summary>Commons Compress cannot be built with JDK14 due to Pack200 removal</summary>
